title: Fiskars
description: Fiskars is known for its distinctive colors, primarily featuring a warm orange (#FF8E00) often associated with robust, durable garden tools. The color palette also includes black (#000000), earthy brown (#955214), a natural green (#55601C), and a deep blue (#005172). These colors can be associated with nature and practicality, aligning with Fiskars' reputation as a trusted brand in the garden and crafting tools industry.
